reviewText: Loved it!--- it's a film I saw 50 years ago--- as a young recruit at Fort Polk Louisiana--- at the Magnolia Theater on post--- thank you very much!

Elke Sommer is sexy and the big three stars of Hogans Heros appear in "similar personas". Very tacky and "not a good movie". Bizarre 60's exploitation thing which might make you want to read more about Bob Crane's private life. That could be interesting.
